title: Privacy Impact Assessments Register
metadatasummary: This dataset is an abridged log of Privacy Impact Assessments (PIAs) conducted by the Information Management and Security Team in 2017. The PIA process, recommended by the Information Commissioner, helps organizations identify and mitigate privacy risks associated with new projects or policies that involve processing personal data.

title: Privacy Impact Assessments Register
metadatasummary: This dataset is an abbreviated version of the Information Management and Security Team's Privacy Impact Assessments log, which records, tracks, and reports on privacy risk assessments for new projects or policies involving personal data processing. The enquiry log reference number and type refer to the reference number used on the central enquiry log and the type of personal data processing the assessment covers, respectively.
